Package org.ginsim.common.document

Class OOoDocumentWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ginsim.common.document.DocumentWriter
      • org.ginsim.common.document.OOoDocumentWriter
  • public class OOoDocumentWriter
extends DocumentWriter
    OOoDocumentWriter is a backend to write OpenDocument text files. Such files are supported by OpenOffice/LibreOffice and recent versions of MS Office.
    Author:
    Aurelien Naldi
    See Also:
    DocumentWriter
